《滚石》将视频形容为“未来新黑色”的视频<ref name="RS1"/>。《时代》杂志的丹尼尔·达达里奥（{{lang|en|Daniel D'Addario}}）称视频是泰勒絲目前为止“最精致”的音乐录影带，视觉效果堪比《[[罪恶之城|罪恶之城]]》<ref>{{cite web|last1=D’Addario|first1=Daniel|title=Watch Taylor Swift’s Star-Studded Music Video for ‘Bad Blood’|url=http://time.com/3854282/taylor-swift-bad-blood-video-billboard-music-awards/|website=Time|accessdate=2015-05-18|date=2015-05-18|archive-date=2017-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518102029/http://time.com/3854282/taylor-swift-bad-blood-video-billboard-music-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[Slate|Slate]]》杂志同意并找到了出自其他影片的灵感：“一路上，他们顶礼膜拜了无数的电影。除了《[[机械战警|机械战警]]》的前提背景，视频还具备《[[罪恶之城|罪恶之城]]》式的审美、致敬《[[电子世界争霸战|电子世界争霸战]]》的光自行车、《[[杀死比尔|杀死比尔]]》式的雪中战斗<ref>{{cite web|last1=Shetty|first1=Sharan|title=Taylor Swift’s "Bad Blood" Video Has Enough Celebrities to Be an Actual Movie|url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2015/05/17/taylor_swift_bad_blood_music_video_kendrick_lamar_and_every_other_celebrity.html|website=Slate|accessdate=2015-05-17|date=2015-05-18|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726123929/http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2015/05/17/taylor_swift_bad_blood_music_video_kendrick_lamar_and_every_other_celebrity.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《公告牌》还发现录影带与[[布兰妮·斯皮尔斯|布兰妮·斯皮尔斯]]的歌曲〈[[中你的毒|中你的毒]]〉和〈[[爱情玩咖|爱情玩咖]]〉有相似之处，这两个音樂錄影帶的導演也是卡恩<ref>{{cite web|last1=Strecker|first1=Erin|title=Taylor Swift's 'Bad Blood' Video: 15 Things We Need To Talk About Right Now|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/bbma/6568620/taylor-swift-bad-blood-video-burning-questions|website=Billboard|accessdate=2015-05-18|date=2015-05-17|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125151158/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/bbma/6568620/taylor-swift-bad-blood-video-burning-questions|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

